### Description

```
@Component({
  selector: 'app-root',
  imports: [NgIf],
  template: `
    <span *ngIf="isServer">This is a SERVER-ONLY content</span>
    <span *ngIf="!isServer">This is a CLIENT-ONLY content</span>
  `,
})
export class App {
  isServer = isPlatformServer(inject(PLATFORM_ID));
  elementRef = inject(ElementRef);

  _ = afterEveryRender(() => {
    console.log('App component rendered');
    console.log('Current content:', this.elementRef.nativeElement.innerHTML);
  });
}
```

In this example `afterEveryRender` only fires once, before hydration. 

